  <brief_title>The Effect of Plant Sterol Supplement on Blood Cholesterol</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single Centre, Randomized Crossover Double-Blind Placebo-Controlled Study to Measure the Effect of Plant Sterol Supplement on Blood Cholesterol</official_title>
